      "value": "gatha2"
    },
    "innerText": "Nimantetvā mahāvīraṃ, dānaṃ datvā mahārahaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Annapānena vatthena, sasaṅghaṃ jinapūjayiṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "11"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "11."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Tassa buddhassa asamassa, cakkaṃ vattitamuttamaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Sutvāna paṇitaṃ dhammaṃ, pabbajjamabhirocayiṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "12"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "12."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Mahādānaṃ pavattetvā, rattindivamatandito;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Pabbajjaṃ guṇasampannaṃ, pabbajiṃ jinasantike."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "13"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "13."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Ācāraguṇasampanno, vattasīlasamāhito;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Sabbaññutaṃ gavesanto, ramāmi jinasāsane."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "14"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "14."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      " ‘‘Saddhāpītiṃ ",
      " upagantvā, buddhaṃ vandāmi sattharaṃ;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Saddhāpītiṃ upagantvā, buddhaṃ vandāmi sattharaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Pīti uppajjati mayhaṃ, bodhiyāyeva kāraṇā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "15"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "15."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Anivattamānasaṃ ñatvā, sambuddho etadabravi;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Ekattiṃse ito kappe, ayaṃ buddho bhavissati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "16"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "16."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Ahu kapilavhayā rammā…pe… hessāma sammukhaṃ imaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "17"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "17."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Tassāhaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā, bhiyyo cittaṃ pasādayiṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Uttariṃ vatamadhiṭṭhāsiṃ, dasapāramipūriyā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "cakkaṃ vattita"
      },
      "nti dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṇītaṃ dhamma"
      },
      "nti uttarimanussadhammaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pabbajjaṃ guṇasampanna"
      },
      "nti ñatvā pabbajinti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vattasīlasamāhito"
      },
      "ti vattesu ca sīlesu ca samāhito. Tesaṃ tesaṃ pūraṇe samāhitoti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ramāmī"
      },
      "ti abhiramiṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saddhāpīti"
      },
      "nti saddhañca pītiñca upagantvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vandāmī"
      },
      "ti abhivandiṃ, atītatthe vattamānavacanaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Satthara"
      },
      "nti satthāraṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anivattamānasa"
      },
      "nti anosakkiyamānamānasaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Tattha cakkaṃ vattitanti dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ. Paṇītaṃ dhammanti uttarimanussadhammaṃ. Pabbajjaṃ guṇasampannanti ñatvā pabbajinti attho. Vattasīlasamāhitoti vattesu ca sīlesu ca samāhito. Tesaṃ tesaṃ pūraṇe samāhitoti attho. Ramāmīti abhiramiṃ. Saddhāpītinti saddhañca pītiñca upagantvā. Vandāmīti abhivandiṃ, atītatthe vattamānavacanaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. Sattharanti satthāraṃ. Anivattamānasanti anosakkiyamānamānasaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Tassa ",
      " pana bhagavato anomaṃ nāma nagaraṃ ahosi. Suppatīto nāmassa pitā khattiyo, yasavatī nāma mātā, soṇo ca uttaro ca dve aggasāvakā, upasanto nāmupaṭṭhāko, rāmā ca samālā ca dve aggasāvikā, sālarukkho bodhi, sarīraṃ saṭṭhihatthubbedhaṃ ahosi. Saṭṭhivassasahassāni āyu, sucittā nāmassa bhariyā, suppabuddho nāmassa putto, suvaṇṇasivikāya nikkhami. Tena vuttaṃ –"
    ],
    "innerText": "Tassa pana bhagavato anomaṃ nāma nagaraṃ ahosi. Suppatīto nāmassa pitā khattiyo, yasavatī nāma mātā, soṇo ca uttaro ca dve aggasāvakā, upasanto nāmupaṭṭhāko, rāmā ca samālā ca dve aggasāvikā, sālarukkho bodhi, sarīraṃ saṭṭhihatthubbedhaṃ ahosi. Saṭṭhivassasahassāni āyu, sucittā nāmassa bhariyā, suppabuddho nāmassa putto, suvaṇṇasivikāya nikkhami. Tena vuttaṃ –"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "18"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "18."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Anomaṃ nāma nagaraṃ, suppatīto nāma khattiyo;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Mātā yasavatī nāma, vessabhussa mahesino."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "23"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "23."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Soṇo ca uttaro ceva, ahesuṃ aggasāvakā;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Upasanto nāmupaṭṭhāko, vessabhussa mahesino."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "24"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "24."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Rāmā ceva samālā ca, ahesuṃ aggasāvikā;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Bodhi tassa bhagavato, mahāsāloti vuccati."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "25"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "25."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "children": [
      " ‘‘Sotthiko ",
      " ceva rammo ca, ahesuṃ aggupaṭṭhakā;"
    ],
    "innerText": "‘‘Sotthiko ceva rammo ca, ahesuṃ aggupaṭṭhakā;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Gotamī sirimā ceva, ahesuṃ aggupaṭṭhikā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "26"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "26."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Saṭṭhiratanamubbedho, hemayūpasamūpamo;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Kāyā niccharatī rasmi, rattiṃva pabbate sikhī."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "27"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "27."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Saṭṭhivassasahassāni, āyu tassa mahesino;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Tāvatā tiṭṭhamāno so, tāresi, janataṃ bahuṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "28"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "28."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Dhammaṃ vitthārikaṃ katvā, vibhajitvā mahājanaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Dhammanāvaṃ ṭhapetvāna, nibbuto so sasāvako."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "hangnum"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "29"
      },
      "."
    ],
    "innerText": "29."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Dassaneyyaṃ sabbajanaṃ, vihāraṃ iriyāpathaṃ;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Sabbaṃ tamantarahitaṃ, nanu rittā sabbasaṅkhārā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "hemayūpasamūpamo"
      },
      "ti ",
      " suvaṇṇatthambhasadisoti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Niccharatī"
      },
      "ti ito cito ca sandhāvati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rasmī"
      },
      "ti pabhārasmi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rattiṃva pabbate sikhī"
      },
      "ti rattiyaṃ pabbatamatthake aggi viya. Raṃsivijjotā tassa kāyeti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vibhajitvā"
      },
      "ti vibhāgaṃ katvā, ugghaṭitādivasena sotāpannādivasena cāti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dhammanāva"
      },
      "nti aṭṭhaṅgamaggasaṅkhātaṃ dhammanāvaṃ, caturoghanittharaṇatthāya ṭhapetvāti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dassaneyya"
      },
      "nti dassanīyo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sabbajana"
      },
      "nti sabbo jano, sasāvakasaṅgho sammāsambuddhoti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vihāra"
      },
      "nti vihāro, sabbattha paccatte upayogavacanaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Tattha hemayūpasamūpamoti suvaṇṇatthambhasadisoti attho. Niccharatīti ito cito ca sandhāvati. Rasmīti pabhārasmi. Rattiṃva pabbate sikhīti rattiyaṃ pabbatamatthake aggi viya. Raṃsivijjotā tassa kāyeti attho. Vibhajitvāti vibhāgaṃ katvā, ugghaṭitādivasena sotāpannādivasena cāti attho. Dhammanāvanti aṭṭhaṅgamaggasaṅkhātaṃ dhammanāvaṃ, caturoghanittharaṇatthāya ṭhapetvāti attho. Dassaneyyanti dassanīyo. Sabbajananti sabbo jano, sasāvakasaṅgho sammāsambuddhoti attho. Vihāranti vihāro, sabbattha paccatte upayogavacanaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "innerText": "Vessabhū kira bhagavā usabhavatīnagare kheme migadāye parinibbāyi. Dhātuyo panassa vippakiriṃsu."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gatha1"
    },
    "innerText": "‘‘Usabhavatipure puruttame, jinavasabho bhagavā hi vessabhū;"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "gathalast"
    },
    "innerText": "Upavanavihare manorame, nirupadhisesamupāgato kirā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "unindented"
    },
    "innerText": "Sesaṃ sabbattha gāthāsu pākaṭamevāti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Vessabhūbuddhavaṃsavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Niṭṭhito ekavīsatimo buddhavaṃso."
  }
]